<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Reply Notification</title>
  <style>
    body{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      min-width:100%;
      font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.5;
      background-color:#FAFAFA;
      color:#222222;
    }
    a{
      color:#000;
      text-decoration:none;
    }
    h1{
      font-size:24px;
      font-weight:700;
      line-height:1.25;
      margin-top:0;
      margin-bottom:15px;
      text-align:center;
    }
    p{
      margin-top:0;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }
    table td{
      vertical-align:top;
    }
    .email-wrapper{
      background-color: #0070f3;
      padding:24px;
      color:#ffffff;
    }
    .email-body{
      padding:24px;
      background-color:#f6f6f6;
      padding:24px;
    }
    .button{
      display:inline-block;
      background-color:#0070f3;
      color:#ffffff;
      font-size:16px;
      font-weight:700;
      text-align:center;
      padding:12px 24px;
      border-radius:4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Hello <%= name %></h1>
  <p>A new reply has been made on your comment in "<%= title %>".</p>
  <p>Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion</p>
  <p>Thank you for being a part of our community.!</p>

</body>
</html>